    <h2><a href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/foundations-of-the-restoration-class-preparation-material-2019/lesson-18-class-preparation-material-latter-day-saint-women-and-the-relief-society?lang=jpn">第20課：神殿の儀式と礼拝<img
